Title: ğŸ–¼ Seizing our country, killing the pilot of the Air Forces of th...
Description: Seizing our country, killing the pilot of the Insurgent Forces of the Armed Forces of Ukraine Oleksiy Mes. He heroically demonstrated his remaining battle in the sky. Twenty-sixth sickle Oleksiy under the hour of defeat of the Russian massive combined missile and air strike, having destroyed three missiles and one strike UAV. Oleksiy took the Ukrainians away from the deadly Russian missiles. Unfortunately, at the cost of a rich life. Oleksiy Mes was a strong and dedicated warrior, a high-class pilot, a leader on earth and in the sky, a good friend, a loving son, a father, a man, a patriot of his land. Twenty virgins On the 5th sickle, his brothers came to say goodbye to him - pilots, commanders and colleagues, friends and colleagues, hundreds of ordinary Ukrainians. A couple of MiG-29s fell from the sky to the fallen pilot. Flight over the procession ended with Oleksiya's fighting friends. By order of the Commander-in-Chief of the Armed Forces of Ukraine, Lieutenant Colonel Oleksiy Mes was posthumously awarded the military rank of Colonel. We have lost a reliable friend and a strong warrior. But they have NOT wasted the strength, will and passion to fight, fight and overcome. In our just justice, we will take revenge on the enemy for everything and everyone. Glory to Ukraine! Glory to the Heroes! This year there are 10 fates since the day of the Ilovaisk tragedy - a day that has become a symbol of the unwavering spirit and heroism of the Ukrainian soldiers, who demonstrated incredible courage and dedication to the Fatherland.Day in memory of the decedents of Ukraine - this is the hour to honor those who died for our freedom and independence. We remember all the warriors who laid down their lives on the battlefield, seizing our land and bowing their heads before the homelands of the dead.
